com.microsoft.bingads.v11.bulk.entities

Class BulkAdGroupRemarketingListAssociation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.bingads.v11.internal.bulk.BulkObject
      • com.microsoft.bingads.v11.bulk.entities.BulkEntity
        • com.microsoft.bingads.v11.internal.bulk.entities.SingleRecordBulkEntity
          • com.microsoft.bingads.v11.bulk.entities.BulkAdGroupRemarketingListAssociation

  • public class BulkAdGroupRemarketingListAssociation
extends SingleRecordBulkEntity
    Represents an Ad Group Remarketing List Association that can be read or written in a bulk file.

    This class exposes the #setAdGroupCriterion and #getAdGroupCriterion methods that can be used to read and write fields of the Ad Group Remarketing List Association record in a bulk file.

    For more information, see Ad Group Remarketing List Association at https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=846127.

    See Also:
    BulkServiceManager, BulkOperation, BulkFileReader, BulkFileWriter
